text: Supplied video obtained Wednesday, October 30, 2019, of Labour leader Jeremy Corbyn speaking in the House of Commons during a debate on the Early Parliamentary General Election Bill. Corbyn says Labour is ready to fight an election. "I'm ready for it. We are ready for it," he says. "Because we want to be able to say to the people of this country, there is an alternative to austerity, there is an alternative to inequality, there is alternative to sweetheart trade deals with Donald Trump." (AAP VIDEO/Supplied/parliamentlive.tv)
